Harel Insurance Investments & Financial Services Ltd Key Developments

Harel Insurance Investments and Financial Services Ltd. Announces Earnings Results for the First Quarter of 2017
May 24 17
Harel Insurance Investments and Financial Services Ltd. announced earnings results for the first quarter of 2017. For the quarter, the company reported total earned premiums and benefit contributions increased by 16% to ILS 5.46 billion compared with ILS 4.7 billion in the corresponding quarter last year. Comprehensive profit was ILS 253 million, compared with ILS 14 million in the corresponding quarter last year. Equity attributed to the company's shareholders was ILS 5.3 billion at March 31, 2017. The return on equity (RoE) was 19%.


Harel Insurance Investments & Financial Services Ltd, Special/Extraordinary Shareholders Meeting, Mar 28, 2017
Mar 23 17
Harel Insurance Investments & Financial Services Ltd, Special/Extraordinary Shareholders Meeting, Mar 28, 2017, at 14:00 Israel Standard Time.


Harel Insurance Investments and Financial Services Ltd. Announces Earnings Results for the Fourth Quarter and Full Year 2016
Mar 23 17
Harel Insurance Investments and Financial Services Ltd. announced earnings results for the fourth quarter and full year 2016. For the fourth quarter, the company has reported strong fourth quarter results, with net profit of ILS 217 million. 

After a poor first half, the company’s comprehensive profit rose 11% to ILS 422 million in 2016.


